CalX Project
CalX is stepper motor controller library and user interface. CalX supports plugins to control different types of devices and instruments using unitified library and interface. System offers different API to operate with motors, allows graph building and limited g-code execution. Current software state is unstable, user interface and library is under development.
Author: Jevgenijs Protopopovs.
Project repo: <https://github.com/protopopov1122/CalX>

